er the\ncritical wall shear stress $\\tau_s$ (yield stress) that is needed to bring the\ngranular media into motion... (see article for a complete abstract).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2018 16:41:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 May 2018 11:46:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 May 2018 14:30:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-16"}
