-15~$ AB\nremain unrealistic. More accurate lens modeling and future observations of\nlensing clusters with the James Webb Space Telescope can reliably extend the UV\nLF to fainter magnitudes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2018 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-25"}
