is\ncapable of generalizing to novel objects. Qualitative results (videos), code,\npre-trained models, and simulation environments are available at\nhttp://vpg.cs.princeton.edu\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Mar 2018 08:31:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2018 03:39:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 30 Sep 2018 20:34:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-02"}
