, which could contribute to the\nobserved population of Galactic hypervelocity stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Mar 2018 14:30:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2018 07:04:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 19 Aug 2018 12:48:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-21"}
