Ar\nwithin the copper housings. These two scenarios are straightforward to test\nthrough assay of the purge gas as well as Monte Carlo and laboratory study of\nthe DAMA/LIBRA copper housings when excited by ionizing radiation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Mar 2018 14:35:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-28"}
